    <h1>Hotel Room Reservation System - Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how our Hotel Room Reservation System ("System") collects, uses, and discloses your information.</p>
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Personal information you provide during reservation, such as name, contact information, and payment details.</li>
            <li>Information collected automatically, such as your IP address, device type, and browsing activity on the System.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To process your reservation requests and provide you with confirmation.</li>
            <li>To improve the System's functionality and user experience.</li>
            <li>To send you communication related to your reservation, including updates and promotions (with your consent).</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us with operating the System, such as payment processors. We will only share the information necessary for them to perform their services.</p>
        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable steps to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no internet transmission is completely secure.</p>
        <h2>Your Choices</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>You can access and update your personal information through your account on the System.</li>
            <li>You can opt out of receiving promotional emails by clicking the unsubscribe link in the emails.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our System is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
        <h2>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on the System.</p>
